194
00:11:09.560 --> 00:11:11.160
-[Cesia] Give it to me!
-[Grześ] No!

195
00:11:11.240 --> 00:11:14.040
-It is the fruit of satanic temptation...
-[Cesia] Come. come.

196
00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:16.320
