239
00:13:48.840 --> 00:13:51.560
Don't remember. I must've been wasted.

240
00:13:51.640 --> 00:13:53.440
-[gunshot]
-Holy fuck!

241
00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.200
[pained groans]

242
